section.section:
A bank, trust company, or savings bank authorized to exercise trust powers under subsection (a)(4) of this section shall file with the Commissioner of Financial Regulation, prior to exercising trust powers in this State, information sufficient to identify:
The correct corporate name of the bank, trust company, or savings bank;
An address and telephone number of a contact person for the bank, trust company, or savings bank;
A resident agent; and
Any additional information considered necessary by the Commissioner for protection of the public.
